aving 1.4mm thickness and\n2cm length, much smaller than Fe-DBA. Conclusion: DBA fabricated from K-edge\nmaterial such as Ho can address count rate problem of PCCT and provide\nminiature size, minimal image artifacts, and improved material decomposition at\nlowest patient dose.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 1 Oct 2016 20:41:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 4 Oct 2016 02:47:03 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 28 Nov 2016 17:36:17 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 22 Dec 2016 16:03:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-12-23"}
