f the dimension down to $O(\\frac{\\log (2+\\varepsilon^2 n)}{\\varepsilon^2})$,\nwhere $n$ is the number of points.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 2 Oct 2016 08:24:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 15 Dec 2016 09:35:32 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 16 Mar 2017 06:26:20 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Sun, 2 Apr 2017 11:44:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-04-04"}
