 provided to the\npiezoelectric array are determined in X-rays, in intra-focal setup at the XACT\nfacility at INAF/OAPA. In this work, we describe the manufacturing steps to\nobtain a first active mirror prototype and the very first test performed in\nX-rays.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 2 Oct 2016 12:51:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-10-04"}
